Package: roundrect
Title: Draw Rounded Rectangles with Independent Corner Radii
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shahriar", "Siham", , "shahriar.siham@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An improved version of the `grid` package's rounded rectangles, 
    allowing each corner to have a different radius instead of a uniform one. 
    This package also provides more intuitive parameter names for easier usage. 
    Customize fill color, border properties, opacity, and more with a simple function call.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    grid
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
